Which do you like better and why?

I can't really drink any of them anymore but I went with Dr. Pepper all the way. Dr. Pepper is way better than Mr. Pibb anyway and all Pibb Extra is is just a soda where they decided to put in extra caffine. That's it. There is nothing else except for extra caffine. Nothing was improved.
 
 
 Also, Dr. Pepper had a commercial with the Meat Loaf song "I'd Do Anything For Love (But I Won't Do That)" so it's better anyway.
I voted Dr. Pepper, but I'm not really sure why. Does regular pibb even exist any longer? I thought they replaced it completely with Pibb extra.

I'm not sure. I sometimes see it in WalMart now and then.
 
 The reason I HATE Pibb Extra is because you leave it in a glass with ice for even 1 minute and already the nice weak watery taste is there, waiting for to spit it right out the moment it hits the air in your mouth.
 
 Dr. Pepper, now THAT has a more endurable flavor. Though I doubt I would drink it without fizz.
I heard that Mr. Pibb had to change its name because it was offensive to those whiny feminists and so they changed it to Pibb Extra. People who get offended over dumb stuff are dumb.
